Superclass for test programs for JImmutables. The main purpose of the Testable is to run its execute method. Each version of the method will first generate a goal size. Then it will grow the JImmutable by a third of that size and shrink it by a sixth. This growing/shrinking repeats six times, until the JImmutable is the generated size. All the values are then deleted.
